===Peterborough United===
Woodhouse signed for [[Peterborough United F.C.|Peterborough United]] on 14 October 2003,<ref name="Posh complete signing of midfielder">{{cite news
| title = Posh complete signing of midfielder
| url = http://www.theposh.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10427~437772,00.html
